{"tid":2451012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應梅根婚禮前秘婚說法 英牧師：僅私人對話 梅根來自美國才不明白","createTime":"2021-03-17T21:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T06:16:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"20981770bbbcd5ea7affd5d643ad57e940579230","tid":2451012,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:36:18.000Z","msg":"否定梅根說法 牧師︰婚禮不能無見證人<br />\n紐卡斯爾教區牧師愛德華茲（Mark Edwards）表示，匿名的聖公會蘭貝思宮（Lambeth Palace）職員向他透露，坎特伯雷大主教「並不會處理私人婚禮，梅根是美國人，所以不會明白」。消息人士又指，韋爾比曾與哈里夫婦在花園就婚禮一事進行私人對話，「但我可以向你保證，在全國直播活動前沒有舉行過婚禮」。<br />\n<br />\n愛德華茲表示，梅根的說法為神職人員和計劃結婚的情侶帶來困惑，指出在英國封城時期，收到不少人查詢可否舉行私人婚禮，但他都被迫拒絕，「然後我要解釋這並非合法的婚禮，亦不是根據教會法」。<br />\n<br />\n愛德華茲續指，這把一眾牧師置於困難處境，人們總是問：「婚禮應否設有見證人或授權或法律指定的人，還是現在只需臨時安排神職人員？我們可以在沒有見證人下在後花園主持私人婚禮？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/LWKVLVEMSJBSPDRBFLG5DNLYNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2FLWKVLVEMSJBSPDRBFLG5DNLYNY%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2Qg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=593a69b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2FLWKVLVEMSJBSPDRBFLG5DNLYNY%2F&h=577e08fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/LWKVLVEMSJBSPDRBFLG5DNLYNY/</a>"},{"pid":"210f862cac64df1514e2be8da8803bd321ce1046","tid":2451012,"uid":173207,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T21:41:49.000Z","msg":"我好奇梅根對教會有咩諗法 之前又話學吓聖詩都唔得 依家又亂講嘢 令好多等結婚嘅人同教會教牧困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00633065944186f7dca939c2cea735b905d2c49b","tid":2451012,"uid":203889,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"210f862cac64df1514e2be8da8803bd321ce1046","tid":2451012,"uid":173207,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-